%% Diagram: Pipeline mental model
%% Type: flowchart
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
flowchart LR
    A["Browser bursts<br/>(unpredictable)"] --> B["Fire-and-forget API<br/>(204, no I/O)"]
    B --> C["Kafka buffer<br/>(absorbs spikes)"]
    C --> D["Dedup window<br/>(70-90% reduction)"]
    D --> E["OLAP storage<br/>(aggregate queries)"]
    E --> F["Dashboards & alerts<br/>(trends, top offenders)"]
